snippet.title: HANUMAN Hindi Teaser | Prasanth Varma Cinematic Universe| RKD Studios| Teja Sajja, VinayR, Varalaxmi
snippet.description:
Presenting the Official Hindi Teaser of our upcoming film "HANUMAN". HANUMAN the first ever multilingual Superhero Film set in the world of Anjandari. The film will Kickstart the Indian MythoVerse franchise with #HanumanTeaser and the film will release in 2023. The Telugu spectacle will release Pan India in Telugu, Hindi, Tamil, Kannada and Malayalam. The film is Written & Directed by the visionary Prasanth Varma and stars Teja Sajja, Varalaxmi Sarathkumar, Amritha Aiyer & Vinay Rai in the lead roles. The film is Presented by RKD Studios and has been produced by K Niranjan Reddy.

snippet.title: स्वतन्त्र पार्टी सरकारमा कि प्रतिपक्षमा ! भरोसामा बदलिएला त रविप्रतिको आशा? | Tamasoma Jyotirgamaya
snippet.description:
Tamasoma Jyotirgamaya #tamasomajyotirgamaya  is one of the most popular television talk shows in the nation. As the name suggests it is an effort to explore the true knowledge on the national and international affairs that matter to the communities and the human race as a whole. The guests of the shows include top political leaderships and renowned figures from different walks of life, mostly associated with the contested affairs. The host of the show is Mr. Tikaram Yatri, the editor-in-chief of AP1HD Television. The broadcast time of the show is Monday (9 to 10 PM).

एपीवानबाट प्रत्येक सोमबार बेलुका ९ बजे प्रसारण हुने तमसो मा ज्योतिर्गमय सकारात्मक सोच,सम्भावना र उज्यालोको खोजी गर्ने बहुचर्चित टेलिभिजन अन्तर्वार्ता हो । जीवन भोगाइका बहुआयामिक रंगको इन्द्रेणी यस कार्य्रक्रममा जुनसुकै क्षेत्रका विज्ञ विष्लेषक तथा उदाहरणीय पात्रलाई अतिथिका रूपमा निम्त्याउने गरिन्छ । राष्ट्रियता र स्वाभिमानको पक्षमा कुनै सम्झौता नगरी विकास र परिवर्तनको पक्षमा आवाज मुखरित गर्नु यस कार्यक्रमको मुख्य उद्देश्य हो ।

Presenter: Tikaram Yatri
Guest: Dr. Arnico Panday

Researcher: Sarose Gautam

snippet.description:
The 2022 PUBG MOBILE Global Championship League stage Group Yellow Day 2 is here! Over the four weeks, the greatest PUBG MOBILE teams in the world will battle to secure their spot in PMGC Finals to #BETHEONE! 
#2022PMGC League consists of 3 stages: Group Stage, Survival Stage, and Last Chance. In the First 3 weeks, 48 teams will battle within their respective groups: Red, Green, and Yellow. Top 3 teams from each group will directly qualify for the PMGC Finals in Jakarta, Indonesia. 4-11th place of each group will advance to the Survival Stage. Their goal is clear: Stay out of the bottom 8 spots to advance to the Last Chance, where they can compete for the last 4 spots in the PMGC Finals!

snippet.title: मंसिर चार कस्को सरकारः ‌ओलीको प्रक्षेपणबारे सवाल-जवाफ | Tamasoma Jyotirgamaya | AP1HD
snippet.description:
Tamasoma Jyotirgamaya is one of the most popular television talk shows in the nation. As the name suggests it is an effort to explore the true knowledge on the national and international affairs that matter to the communities and the human race as a whole. The guests of the shows include top political leaderships and renowned figures from different walks of life, mostly associated with the contested affairs. The host of the show is Mr. Tikaram Yatri, the editor-in-chief of AP1HD Television. The broadcast time of the show is Monday (9 to 10 PM).

एपीवानबाट प्रत्येक सोमबार बेलुका ९ बजे प्रसारण हुने तमसो मा ज्योतिर्गमय सकारात्मक सोच,सम्भावना र उज्यालोको खोजी गर्ने बहुचर्चित टेलिभिजन अन्तर्वार्ता हो । जीवन भोगाइका बहुआयामिक रंगको इन्द्रेणी यस कार्य्रक्रममा जुनसुकै क्षेत्रका विज्ञ विष्लेषक तथा उदाहरणीय पात्रलाई अतिथिका रूपमा निम्त्याउने गरिन्छ । राष्ट्रियता र स्वाभिमानको पक्षमा कुनै सम्झौता नगरी विकास र परिवर्तनको पक्षमा आवाज मुखरित गर्नु यस कार्यक्रमको मुख्य उद्देश्य हो ।

Presenter: Tikaram Yatri
Guest: KP Oli

Researcher: Sarose Gautam
Program Co-Ordinator : Kamala Subedi

Editor: Subin Dahal
Studio Producer: Chiranjibi Gautam and Subash Thapa

snippet.title: The Perfect Date - Amit Bhadana | Katrina Kaif
snippet.description:
Get real skills to create a remarkable impact in Software Development and Data Science. Check Out: https://www.scaler.com/?utm_source=brandedcontent&utm_medium=AmitBhadana&utm_campaign=brand_scaler_academy_brandedcontent_AmitBhadana_branded-content-video-campaign-AmitBhadana-05November2022_india_all&utm_content=YT-description

Jab Amit ko nahi mili mannchahi naukari, he started looking out for a chokari, for marriage. Par kismat ne shayad kasam kha rakhi thi ki vo badlegi hi nahi. Chor bazaar se Amit lata hai ek phone aur iska cross connection ho jata hai phone ki asli owner “Kay” ke sath. Amit full tayyari karke date par pahunch jata hai par aisa kuch nahi hota jo usne socha hota hai, aur jo hota hai vo kisi ne bhi nahi socha hota. Kya iss date ke baad Amit ko milegi Mrs. Bhadana? Video dekh kar khud jaan jao na. There is nothing perfect about this date but comedy hai up to date. 
Enjoy this rib tickler with your whole family.
